Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见一个好漂亮的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在乐园计划中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.75,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,663)}Arcadian Project
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保有星核的机构共有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中第二ALVIS·蓬莱岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阿瓦隆之名编入新联合国后消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三ALVIS·海神岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以亚特兰蒂斯之名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编入新联合国后行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正在周边海域搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能供5千人居住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与牵牛星的通信才是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是与人类军交涉的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现岛屿 立即进行登陆作战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好最大限度的战斗力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄美姐 该体检了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再发作就撑不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在岛上就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感谢 这座让我们一家生活过的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SDP一致
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都是增幅现象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始移植卡诺恩系统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以驾驶这个容器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚改良过的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到坚强的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那女孩的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她指引了我和你们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是她的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好珍惜使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚起床又困了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别硬撑 启动的负荷都转给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是满身疮痍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不该不去什么岛外面的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广登说能见识世界是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知晓了传播和平的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有消耗生命的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消耗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别驾驶了 全都交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见到了之前对岛扔炸弹的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护我们而牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人让给我的生命 我不会舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了 做点吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这就是一骑咖喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿晖咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话请用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:15.27,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(70,30)}希望能在…工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:15.27,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(110,30)}希望岛上和平 真壁一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:15.27,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(150,30)}希望能见到乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有进步嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还远远比不上一骑学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在营地人家也这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.90,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(70,30)\fad(0,400)}希望岛上和平 真壁一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:31.03,note5,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38\pos(70,30)\fad(400,0)}活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我可不想输他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚瑠岛部队发来报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对照 第三ALVIS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是你们的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢这座岛的核
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 新的星核正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是牺牲了一万七千人才运来的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新衣服 好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都给你 换给我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以守护美三香和大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会守护大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到这就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能以后会麻烦你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和爸爸等你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了我们三个一起吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去吗 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回来哦 美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听见吗 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收讯良好 叫我的代号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 座天使1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请护送登陆部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 遵从阁下的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海神岛 距离10
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生体反应和敌影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护盾也没有展开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登陆开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和须佐之男 月读 十二号机待命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登陆部队 更新位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步行者出现了就以天照和零号机应战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去另一座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人也没有星核
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了你们找到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是敌人 是遭到了人类的袭击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样 隐藏了敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步行者及大量敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往海神岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有朝本岛来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是看准了刚登陆之后的时机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 各机掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天照 SDP启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到 你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我会守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你有觉得天空很美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看的不是未来 而是许多的现在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到你了 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快避开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反弹回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全机 掩护零号机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步行者反射了零号机的炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对抗计划被看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被其他存在同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和之前是不同的敌人 史彦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------STAF----------------------------
